'''Okukuseku''' is a variety of [[gin]]-like alcoholic drink originating in West Africa. It is especially popular in [[Ghana]] and [[Nigeria]].

The drink has lent its name to a popular Ghanaian musical group, [[Okukuseku (band)|Okukuseku]].

